==English==

===Verb===
'''to prepare'''  ([[prepares]], [[prepared]], [[preparing]])

[[Transitive]]:
# to make [[ready]] for a [[specific]] [[event]]
#* we '''prepared''' the [[spacecraft]] for [[takeoff]]
# to [[put]] [[together]] [[various]] [[element]]s to make [[something]]
#* we '''prepared''' a [[meal]] from [[whatever]] was [[available]]

[[Intransitive]]:
# to make [[oneself]] or [[thing]]s ready
#* we '''prepared''' for a [[bump]]y [[ride]]
# to [[study]] at a [[preparatory school]] (UK only?)
===Translation===
to put together to make
